{"tid":1455324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[十萬火急]機場義士快撤!!","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:11:43.000Z","uid":280457,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"546217948f8afb9954ef2fb5a6341fbe615f84ea","tid":1455324,"uid":280457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:54:04.000Z","msg":"P牌仔第一之開POST<br />\n我有朋友入左去機場，我本來想入但有事行唔開<br />\n剛問過另外而家在機場做野既朋友<br />\n佢話睇到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">T1禁區好撚多狗準備緊</span></span>!!!<br />\n真係唔知等D機停哂同出去交通停哂後會發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n麻煩你地真係認真考慮要即時離開!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">千萬唔好落單<br />\n可以的話同埋D人一齊放工&hellip;我朋友話再遲可能要行出東涌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好負皮我&hellip;&hellip;我真係唔想任何一個出事!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5f3a5cd13696ffda5a0a49135865bb436666e2","tid":1455324,"uid":264455,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fa19c0e823d8cad48c2b1265b99e703406be4c","tid":1455324,"uid":280457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff5f3a5cd13696ffda5a0a49135865bb436666e2","tid":1455324,"uid":264455,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母你又知我除左今日外日日都涼緊冷氣?<br />\n咁樣俾狗圍出事你覺得好安樂係咪?"},{"pid":"f9ff2968d80781407ddfeb29b255b94273391f3f","tid":1455324,"uid":165246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:01:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">走呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr